body:
With this PR, the tracking reconstruction has been introduced in the 2023 scenario with both the tilted (2023tilted workflow) and the flat (2023GReco workflow) tracker geometry. 
In order to fix also the Lorentz Angle message for the tilted, this PR should be integrated together with cms-data/SLHCUpgradeSimulations-Geometry#2.

